    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and usage. While the engine and transmission are functional and get you from A to B, you should expect some cosmetic wear on the exterior paint and noticeable thinning or staining on the interior upholstery. There are a few minor mechanical quirks that don't prevent driving but may require attention down the road, such as a noisy suspension over bumps and an aging battery. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a car with a bit of character and history.",
