      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved and looked after, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! If you're looking for a dependable car that still feels great on the road, this is the one. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come by and take it for a test drive!",
